1005303-CN8X7RUv.png"><div class=3D"project-info"><h3>A Software Program Th=
at Solves a Real Client's Daily Problem</h3><p>A Grade Tracker app I built =
to help a teacher keep up with missing and late work in one clean view. The=
 dashboard shows totals at the top =E2=80=94 total entries, missing, late, =
turned in, and average grade =E2=80=94 and a table below where each row tra=
cks a student's assignment, due date, status, and grade, with color-coded l=
abels so problems are easy to spot. The teacher can add new rows, change st=
atus, and update grades as work comes in. I built this to solve a real prob=
lem for a real client and to learn how to turn messy daily paperwork into a=
 simple, organized tool that actually saves them time.</p><div class=3D"tec=
